10\. Outbound Emails

  


Requirements

The LoadHawk Solution sends the following outbound emails. These emails are generated as email merges, with a hard-coded signature at the bottom.

  


The signature contains the following: 

  * GemWood logo
  * The following details: 
    * 606-282-8957 or 606-282-3865
    * [gemwood@timberdriven.com](mailto:gemwood@timberdriven.com)
    * 1518 Allen Road
    * Waynesburg, KY 40489
